# Google OAuth Client ID (required for Google Drive sync).
# Create at https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials
# Enable "Google Drive API" + create OAuth 2.0 Client ID (Web).
# Add your app's origin to "Authorized JavaScript origins".
#
# Each user signs in with THEIR OWN Google account — this Client ID only
# identifies the app to Google. Users' data goes to their own Drive.
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=""
